data.description: What a fantastic neighborhood, location, Pool, parks, sports courts and more! Enjoy a beautiful and spacious backyard, with view fencing of the greenbelt, fully extended patio, fountain and pavers. Perfect spot for your morning coffee! Spa/Jacuzzi included.  Kitchen includes a gas stove and a double oven. The large primary bathroom offers a separate tub and shower, toilet door for privacy, and with double sinks. Primary bedroom in this split floorplan includes a walk-in closet. Two bonus rooms in the house, one could be a 4th bedroom. All appliances are included, and the home has a water softener. Wonderfully located Maricopa neighborhood and a quality-built Taylor Morrisona home awaits you. Dual air conditioners. Glennwilde community offers pool, spa, parks and playgrounds
